videos.headline: Georgia Southern takes lead with 12-yard TD pass
videos.description: Georgia Southern QB Kevin Ellison throws a 12-yard touchdown pass to BJ Johnson III, giving the Eagles' the lead over Troy.

videos.headline: Ellison takes it himself for 54-yard score
